{"tid":707214,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[多重選擇遊戲書] 2018世界盃：宿命對決","createTime":"2018-06-18T13:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T06:59:52.000Z","uid":180575,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2ca8317c7843e2dd96d853b28bbd29ad8bc00e6d","tid":707214,"uid":180575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:33:29.000Z","msg":"我係Medium出左個關於今屆世界盃題材嘅免費網頁遊戲書叫「2018世界盃：宿命對決」，有多重分支選擇同唔同結局。<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@macadan/2018worldcuptc0528-ae893e994826\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40macadan%2F2018worldcuptc0528-ae893e994826&d=yJkwUUo9IwlvwuXHazeU8f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=2db12870\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@macadan/2018worldcuptc0528-ae893e994826</a><br />\n<br />\n故事比你成為球王，你所做嘅每個決定都會影響你能否帶領葡萄牙隊奪得2018年世界盃冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n全故事共有N個Bad Ending、1個Good Ending、1個Neutral Ending和1個Sad Ending，仲加左蝴蝶效應元素，請你自己試試點爆機&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢類玩法嘅實體遊戲書曾於80年代在西方流行，依家我想以新穎的題材和網頁書的形式去重新呈現呢種舊文化。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎轉載，謝謝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請追蹤我的Medium和Facebook專頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@macadan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40macadan&d=yJkwUUo9IwlvwuXHazeU8f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=ab19d1c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@macadan</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/continuehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcontinuehk%2F&d=yJkwUUo9IwlvwuXHazeU8f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=6d94b7c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/continuehk/</a>"},{"pid":"874534d45e763f452c53603363afdb67fd54d3ea","tid":707214,"uid":56589,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:47:15.000Z","msg":"Idea唔錯<br />\n題材一般<br />\n名on9"},{"pid":"9bc8fc2dcd2c15e035102c59447f115ebdc495d9","tid":707214,"uid":180575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"874534d45e763f452c53603363afdb67fd54d3ea","tid":707214,"uid":56589,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:47:15.000Z","msg":"Idea唔錯<br />\n題材一般<br />\n名on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:56:25.000Z","msg":"用世界盃題材只係小試牛刀<br />\n實戰試下遊戲書製作有乜難題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n長遠我希望能用原創長篇故事去搞更過癮嘅遊戲書<br />\n<br />\n個名同最後幾個結局有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330aab67ebd4f5d328b190a91c63ccf18222203d","tid":707214,"uid":11785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T16:20:35.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前好鐘意睇呢類型嘅書"},{"pid":"b145043a29ec729d1647afa1e2d5302c1048e655","tid":707214,"uid":180575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"330aab67ebd4f5d328b190a91c63ccf18222203d","tid":707214,"uid":11785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T16:20:35.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前好鐘意睇呢類型嘅書"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T16:25:22.000Z","msg":"我細個係兒童圖書館睇過實體遊戲書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3db76a7d61dd800b53fd3833f5aa2ab099365b3","tid":707214,"uid":180575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T16:29:47.000Z","msg":"對於較年輕嘅巴絲<br />\n不妨認識下乜係遊戲書<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/游戏书\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E4%B9%A6&d=yJkwUUo9IwlvwuXHazeU8f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=58a53ab7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/游戏书</a>"},{"pid":"ab2c8e677a137b11e373b68a4ee42099f903d580","tid":707214,"uid":43669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T17:21:29.000Z","msg":"想做好人都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 返工良物<br />\n幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f65b269f7fd8fa125245e4b13b6332be32eca21","tid":707214,"uid":65816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T17:45:18.000Z","msg":"Idea幾好，但啲劇情好撚戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da165244f1ac2864740c5c4e3c653356de51a0cb","tid":707214,"uid":180575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab2c8e677a137b11e373b68a4ee42099f903d580","tid":707214,"uid":43669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T17:21:29.000Z","msg":"想做好人都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 返工良物<br />\n幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T18:18:39.000Z","msg":"整體黎講都想鼓勵大家做好人<br />\n始終足球運動都係正面野<br />\n但同時又加左好多fake玩家嘅劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家玩完後能印象深刻少少<br />\n<br />\n睇Medium嘅stat<br />\n暫時16x人睇過第1頁<br />\nGood Ending個頁得20人睇過<br />\n共有58頁<br />\n無論你點走都係得1頁係Good Ending<br />\n可以當係走迷宮咁<br />\n又有故事睇可打發下時間<br />\n<br />\n網頁版遊戲書係會幾適合用手機玩<br />\n如裝埋Medium個app黎玩效果會更好<br />\n因為如係網頁玩<br />\n襟每個超連結會開新視窗<br />\n如係Medium個app內玩<br />\n襟超連結唔會開新視窗"},{"pid":"d9f63a519e40b064cdf18e554200d8562778920b","tid":707214,"uid":180575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f65b269f7fd8fa125245e4b13b6332be32eca21","tid":707214,"uid":65816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T17:45:18.000Z","msg":"Idea幾好，但啲劇情好撚戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T18:31:08.000Z","msg":"初頭如揀轉會中超球會路線<br />\n我係特別加得多on9劇情<br />\n極戲劇化同荒謬<br />\n<br />\non9野有D鋪排到同Good Ending結局有關<br />\n都唔on9得哂架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b11c7b940088eeb8ed974c0d5a5f1ada914c9f5","tid":707214,"uid":180575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T18:42:10.000Z","msg":"剩計第1頁幾個鐘已237人襟過入去睇<br />\n係暫時我係Medium上最多人睇嘅一篇文<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/023848_a98f2f696b4cd5b15552cd0df134ec7d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F023848_a98f2f696b4cd5b15552cd0df134ec7d.png&h=3d763cad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n襟過入結局3種Ending嘅人數<br />\nNeutral Ending: 52人<br />\nGood Ending: 33人<br />\nBad Ending: 38人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/023909_4a41bab34ed80275b7d7ea215b5a4725.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F023909_4a41bab34ed80275b7d7ea215b5a4725.png&h=12cf6a5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"593fdc5040c31b23efcebb4e602329bbeafdf61a","tid":707214,"uid":180575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T18:44:10.000Z","msg":"上高打錯左<br />\n唔係Bad Ending<br />\n係Sad Ending<br />\n<br />\nYOU FAILED或YOU DIED個類先係Bad Ending<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全部有得back番上個選擇唔駛由頭玩過"},{"pid":"ee6ab7ad8d083bf32bf289ce550b3dbfd41d8547","tid":707214,"uid":180575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:37:26.000Z","msg":"呢度有冇人順利玩到Good Ending?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b792afdde4be6350921a73269d702e4de6b4c4","tid":707214,"uid":180575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇Medium統計<br />\n第1頁已有446人睇過<br />\n<br />\n現實中阿根廷險晉級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遊戲書內你能否帶領葡萄牙遇上阿根廷呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}